            "q1_question": "Does this actually work on cracked heels?",
            "q1_answer": "Yes — and we back it with a 30-day money-back guarantee. Most customers see noticeably softer, hydrated feet after one 30-minute session. For deeply cracked heels, plan on 2–3 weekly applications. If it doesn't work for you, we refund you in full.",
